
Overview of noun spade

The noun spade has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (2) spade -- (a playing card in the major suit that has one or more black figures on it; "she led a low spade"; "spades were trumps")
2. (1) spade -- (a sturdy hand shovel that can be pushed into the earth with the foot)
3. nigger, nigga, spade, coon, jigaboo, nigra -- ((ethnic slur) extremely offensive name for a Black person; "only a Black can call another Black a nigga")

